node.text: Back in 2018 I went behind the scenes on a very special project with the legendary Sir David Attenborough and @wwf_uk. The trailer for David Attenborough: A Life On Our Planet is out now - it’s going to be his greatest story yet. Can’t wait to watch!🌍 #AttenboroughFilm
